<noinclude>{{month|July}}
Events that occurred on 26 July

==On Earth==
</noinclude>
* '''[[1956]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[Letter 191]].
* '''[[1973]]''' - [[wikipedia:John Giffard, 3rd Earl of Halsbury|Lord Halsbury]] visits [[J.R.R. Tolkien]].
* '''[[1980]]''' - [[Mythcon 11]] at [[wikipedia:University of Nevada, Reno|University of Nevada]], [[wikipedia:Reno, Nevada|Reno]].
* '''[[1981]]''' - The twenty-first episode of the [[The Lord of the Rings (1981 radio series)|1981 radio series]] of ''[[The Lord of the Rings]]'' is aired on [[BBC|BBC Radio 4]].
* '''[[1985]]''' - [[Mythcon 16]] in [[wikipedia:Wheaton, Illinois|Wheaton]], [[wikipedia:Illinois|Illinois]].
* '''[[1987]]''' - [[Mythcon 18]] at [[Marquette University]], [[wikipedia:Milwaukee|Milwaukee]].
* '''[[1991]]''' - [[Mythcon 22]] in [[wikipedia:San Diego|San Diego]], [[wikipedia:California|California]].
* '''[[1996]]''' - [[Mythcon 27]] at [[wikipedia:University of Colorado at Boulder|University of Colorado]] in [[wikipedia:Boulder, Colorado|Boulder, Colorado]].
* '''[[2002]]''' - [[Mythcon 33]] at [[wikipedia:Boulder, Colorado|Boulder]], [[wikipedia:Colorado|Colorado]].
* '''[[2003]]''' - [[Mythcon 34]] in [[wikipedia:Nashville, Tennessee|Nashville]], [[wikipedia:Tennessee|Tennessee]].
* '''[[2009]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing]] 2009 in [[wikipedia:Rieneck|Rieneck]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2012]]''' - ''[[The Saga of Hrolf Kraki]]'', translated by [[Stella M. Mills]], is published in a new edition, with a Foreword by [[Priscilla Tolkien]].
* '''[[2014]]''' - [[Laocoon]], one of Tolkien's favourite trees, lost two limbs. Subsequently, the Oxford Botanic Garden decided that the tree must be felled for safety reasons.
